ams.jhtml|title=CMT : Videos : John Prine, Holly Williams : I'm Telling You (feat. Holly Williams)|publisher=[[Country Music Television]]|accessdate=September 16, 2016|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160917082236/http://www.cmt.com/videos/john-prine/1546089/im-telling-you-feat-holly-williams.jhtml|archive-date=September 17, 2016|url-status=live}}</ref><br />{{small|(featuring [[Holly Williams]])}}\n| Joshua Britt and Neilson Hubbard\n|-\n| 2016\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Color of the Blues'' featuring Susan Tedeschi<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aAYoWePzQ2c|title=John Prine \u2013 Color of the Blues featuring Susan Tedeschi|publisher=[[Oh Boy Records]]|accessdate=June 11, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190605150156/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aAYoWePzQ2c|archive-date=June 5, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| Joshua Britt and Neilson Hubbard\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=\"row\"| ''Sweet Revenge''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t9ADVQNvkB4|title=John Prine \u2013 Sweet Revenge|publisher=[[Oh Boy Records]]|accessdate=June 11, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401104309/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=t9ADVQNvkB4&gl=US&hl=en|archive-date=April 1, 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| Oh Boy Records\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=\"row\"| ''In Spite of Ourselves''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v-YzlbgEOOA|title=John Prine and Iris Dement \u2013 In Spite of Ourselves|publisher=[[Oh Boy Records]]|accessdate=June 11, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190510170626/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v-YzlbgEOOA|archive-date=May 10, 2019|url-status=live}}</ref>\n| Oh Boy Records\n|-\n| 2018\n! scope=\"row\"| ''The Road to 'The Tree of Forgiveness' ''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lPBoRxqTEtM|title=John Prine \u2013 The Road to 'The Tree of Forgiveness'|publisher=[[Oh Boy Records]]|accessdate=June 11, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111004508/https://www.y